=== Joining Multiple Query Criteria with Boolean Operators ===
=== Finding All  ===
=== Special Characters ===

=== Recipe에서 search 사용하기 ===
{{{#!plain
search (:node, "*:*") do |matching_node|
	puts matching_node.to_s
end
}}}

